    narr:narration """This hub tracks the document's reliance on [triadic rhetorical structures](narr:StyleObs_rule_of_three) to anchor complex value propositions. The pattern manifests as a tool for cognitive efficiency, appearing in [product pillar definitions](narr:StyleObs_RuleOfThree_UseCases) and [technical feature sets](narr:Observation_GitNativeTriad) that leverage parallel suffixes for memorability. Beyond simple lists, the device is used to [frame developer-centric workflows](narr:StyleObs_10) at critical decision points. While the rule of three serves as a primary cadence, the document occasionally [stretches the rhythm](narr:StyleObs_6) to accommodate more complex, five-item taxonomies, suggesting that the triadic form is a baseline rather than a rigid constraint. The most aggressive application of the pattern remains the [escalating-severity triad](narr:StyleObs_RuleOfThree), which uses the structure to contrast the utility of AI across different seniority levels.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Observation_GitNativeTriad> ;
